                                                      function
                                                      
->function is a most powerful topic of eny programing
language function provides reasability

->using of function we can reduce our code
,using we can code par our nested
,so we can seve our development time.

ther are 2 types of function:
(1) built in function
(2) user-difined function
---------------------------------
(1) built in function:
->e.g   printf();  scanf(); , getchar(); , getch(); ......

(2)user difined function:
-> that function which is created by user for there requirement.
----------------------------------
-> how to creat function
 
there are 3 staps to follow in creating function time
---------------------------------
stap 1: function declaration

syntex:
        <returntype> funnam();
----------------------------------
stap 2:  function defination

-> main block of code which represent
funtion exequtation

syntex:
     <retrotype> funnam();
        {
            // block of code
        }
---------------------------------        
stap.3: funtion calling
syntex:
        funnam();
=========================================

ther are mainly 4 type of function categories
(1)function whitout paraametes without return types
  syntex:
  void funnum()
  {

  }

(2)function with parameter without return types
syntex:
void funnum(parameters,parameters)
{

}

(3)function without parameter with returntypes
syntex:
reterntype funnum()
{
  return value;
}

(4)function with parameter with return type
syntex:

returntype funnum(parameters,parameters)
  {
    retunr value;
  }

